content: Petrolia is a really fun open world FPS. It's a pretty cool idea that is original and I don't think I have seen in any other game. Petrolia is a game where you are a leader of a country in Africa and rebels attack cities. Obviously, you have to defeat the rebels. You can build things like planes, building, tanks, military bases, and more. You need to control what you produce to make money to build these things. You can grow food, get water, and get oil. I would say more but 500 letters.
